
Apache Benchmark:
    Run a benchmark test ("ab -c 50 -n 500 localhost:3000/fast"):
    -c 50: Concurrency, 50 requests at the same time (ensure 50 requests are always running)
    -n 500: Number, 500 requests total

PM2:
    Using PM2 ("pm2 start index.cluster.pm2.js -i 0"):
    -i 0: pm2 descides how many instances to create for you

    Stop PM2 ("pm2 delete index.cluster.pm2")

    Get a list of running instances ("pm2 list")

    Get more detailed information on an instance ("pm2 show index.cluster.pm2")

    Monitor the process ("pm2 monit")

